recipesJson.name: Nanaberry Custard
recipesJson.author: Zugmaschine
recipesJson.description:
[p]
I love the Strawnana from Ken O`Where, what inspired me to make this Recipe.
[/p]
MTL in my Squape E, with 1.2 Ohm and 15 Watts ....... I LOVE  IT!
Is still good as Shake&Vape( because the 2 Custards are Quick Steeper), 
but give it 3 days to come together.

NOTES: (not complete)
U can sub the SB with  Strawberry Sweet from Jungle Flavour.

Update 28.03.18
Have changed the Strawberry to Capellas Sweet Strawberry and increased  Loarans BC to 4%!
